cell.p:
E kaheaia na halawai a ka Aha Hooko e ka
                                                  Peresidena ma ke noi a kekahi mau hoa 3, o ua Aha
                                                  Hooko la;

Meetings of the executive council shall be called
                                                  by the president, at the request of any three
                                                  members of said council;
